"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-olympics-paris-swimming-usa-habits-b2586582.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  One two-time Olympic champion says she does it 'in every single pool I have swam in'  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 407, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Team USA swimmershave revealed the one \\\"foul\\\" habit they do in \\\"every\\\" pool as they aim to bring home the gold from theParis 2024 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 408, \"to\": 576, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 432, \"end\": 440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9988390326738721, \"rank\": 0.001152947250167657, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Water levels in the La D\\u00e9fense Arena may be rising slightly higher over the coming weeks asseveral Olympiansmade this stark admission: they always pee in the pool.\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 741, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 598, \"end\": 608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_D\\u00e9fense\", \"score\": 0.9929962766529531, \"rank\": 0.007053121458368007, \"text\": \"La D\\u00e9fense\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_D\\u00e9fense\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_D\\u00e9fense\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletes gave several excuses as to why they elect to do their business underwater rather than hop out to the bathroom when nature calls.\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 884, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Zach Harting, whocompeted for the US at the Tokyo Olympics, told theWall Street Journalthat it was the tightness of his polyester bottoms that first made him turn to the aqua loo.\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 886, \"end\": 898, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zach_Harting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zach Harting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zach_Harting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zach_Harting\"}, {\"begin\": 920, \"end\": 922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9877381124586803, \"rank\": 0.012382786115319436, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The world changed for me,\\\" he admitted.\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1107, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For someswimmers, getting into their ultra-tight suits can take up to 20 minutes, also contributing to the need to do their business while wearing them.\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1261, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another Tokyo Olympian Jack Mitchell attributed it to drinking so much fluids - and what goes in, must come out.\", \"from\": 1263, \"to\": 1375, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1271, \"end\": 1285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tokyo Olympian\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1286, \"end\": 1290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\", \"score\": 0.981660306493081, \"rank\": 0.018650672767174182, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\"}, {\"begin\": 1291, \"end\": 1299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leilani_Mitchell\", \"score\": 0.8438764547766646, \"rank\": 0.18500715810054993, \"text\": \"Mitchell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leilani_Mitchell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leilani_Mitchell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I always have to pee,\\\" Mitchell told theJournal.\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1426, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1401, \"end\": 1409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leilani_Mitchell\", \"score\": 0.8438764547766646, \"rank\": 0.18500715810054993, \"text\": \"Mitchell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leilani_Mitchell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leilani_Mitchell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Because I am so hydrated.\\\"\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1453, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These days, professional swimmers rarely think twice when they feel the urge to empty their bladders.\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1556, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, only 40 per cent of adults admit to taking a leak in between doing lengths, one survey of 3,100 people from Healthy Pools found.\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1697, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It sounds so gross to outsiders, but because there is so much chlorine you do not even think about it,\\\" two-time Olympian Katie Hoff told the outlet.\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1849, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1813, \"end\": 1821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999860119716, \"rank\": 1.3987680674976805e-08, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 1822, \"end\": 1832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Hoff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katie Hoff\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Hoff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Hoff\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While two-time Olympic gold medalist Lilly King says she pees in \\\"every single pool I have swam in\\\".\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 1951, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1894, \"end\": 1898, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monarch\", \"score\": 0.7495115247638023, \"rank\": 0.25386126112041807, \"text\": \"King\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monarch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monarch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's just how it goes,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 1989, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"King also revealed she has something of a special gift.\", \"from\": 1991, \"to\": 2046, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can actually pee as I am swimming,\\\" she said of her multitasking abilities.\", \"from\": 2047, \"to\": 2125, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Due to the lack of time before a race, Hoff revealed that some do not even wait to get in the water.\", \"from\": 2127, \"to\": 2227, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2166, \"end\": 2170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Hoff\", \"score\": 0.771854134037975, \"rank\": 0.1901694601318439, \"text\": \"Hoff\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Hoff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Hoff\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She recalled one instance when she was sitting next to a fellow American swimmer and \\\"literally saw it roll down her leg and hit the floor\\\".\", \"from\": 2229, \"to\": 2369, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2293, \"end\": 2301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999702212255849, \"rank\": 1.630890417931565e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is however one golden rule to taking a leak in the pool: do not do it when anyone is in close proximity.\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2481, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You never want to swim through a warm patch,\\\" four-time Olympic medalist Cullen Jones said, otherwise \\\"you are crop dusting everyone\\\".\", \"from\": 2483, \"to\": 2618, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2557, \"end\": 2569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cullen_Jones\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cullen Jones\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cullen_Jones\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cullen_Jones\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's foul,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 2620, \"to\": 2645, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2877, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2698, \"end\": 2709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 0.9999999997160103, \"rank\": 2.795368113681466e-10, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"